description: Newly constructed in 2020 this stunning home offers 2 bedrooms plus a den/office, 2 full bathrooms, approx. 1,256 Sq. Ft of open concept living space and soaring 9'+ celings. The kitchen features white quartz counters, sleek two-tone Europeans style cabinets and stainless steel appliances! Off the living room, through two sets of sliding glass doors you will find an expansive covered deck with recessed lighting. The spacious primary suite is complete with multiple large closets and a beautiful spa like en-suite bathroom. The large guest bedroom has a huge custom built out closet and access to the second full bathroom just outside the door. Additional features include in unit washer/dryer, garage parking, elevator and high efficiency Navien On-Demand system. The building is located directly between East and West Broadway so you are just steps to everything the neighborhood has to offer!
